Turning the farming implement over in his hands, Cody was impressed by its sharpness and heft. "This could really hurt
someone," he said to Lulu, who wagged her tail eagerly, possibly at the prospect of hurting someone. "Why would the
restaurant leave something like this lying around?" His musing was interrupted by his noticing for the first time a
third way out of the room, a small entranceway not far from the door.
